    <h2>Matrimandir</h2>
    <p>At the very center of Auroville, one finds the “soul of the city”, the Matrimandir. Situated in a large open area called the “Peace Area”, from where the future township (which aims to host 50,000 inhabitants) will radiate outwards. The Matrimandir can be viewed as a large golden lotus which is emerging out of the earth, symbolizing the birth of a new consciousness upon earth. The Mother gave a clear instruction about the central meditation room called the inner chamber. The Matrimandir is composed of the inner chamber and 12 small meditation rooms, called petals further surrounded by the 12 Gardens.
    </p>
