    <h2>Sri Aurobindo & The Mother on Integral Yoga</h2>
    <p>Integral Yoga is a methodology developed by Sri Aurobindo and The Mother, for not only exploring the profound depths and heights of human psyche but also for an integral evolutionary transformation of the human nature.
    </p>
    <figure>
        <img class="img-fluid mx-auto d-block" src="/images/mother-aurboindo.png" alt="">
        <figcaption class="text-center">The Mother (Mirra Alfassa) and Sri Aurobindo</figcaption>
    </figure>
    <p>The Fundamental Realisations of Integral Yoga</p>
    <ol>
        <li><i>The psychic change so that a complete devotion can be the main motive of the heart and the ruler of thought, life and action in constant union with the Mother and in her Presence.
        </i></li>
        <li><i>The descent of the Peace, Power, Light etc. of the Higher Consciousness through the head and heart into the whole being, occupying the very cells of the body.
        </i></li>
        <li><i>The perception of the One and Divine infinitely everywhere, the Mother everywhere and living in that infinite consciousness.
        </i><br>– Letters on Yoga, Sri Aurobindo
        </li>
    </ol>
    <p>At the time of Auroville’s founding Mother chose French architect Roger Anger to be the chief architect for Auroville. After drafting several town planning models Roger proposed the “Galaxy” model which was accepted by the Mother and became the base of master plan of Auroville today.
    </p>
